  "texts": [
    "This definition and taxonomy can be used by scholars seeking to address research questions on DeFi and by practitioners who want to actively use the DeFi ecosystem.A taxonomy is a system for classifying and organizing subjects.",
    "In doing so, it helps to understand a set of subjectspecific concepts and creates a nomenclature for those concepts.",
    "A taxonomy facilitates the generation of knowledge as it creates a common language and thus reduces misunderstandings [11].",
    "Therefore it enhances the efficiency of dealing with a particular subject.",
    "No such system exists for DeFi yet, hampering the generation of tacit knowledge of the subject."
  ],
